ic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/5340/', '', 'Acetaminophen, Dextropropoxyphene, Ibuprofen, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone, Benzonatate, Clofedanol, Pentoxyverine', 'Acetylsalicylic acid, Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Codeine', 1767369485);
